texts.content: {"text":"3. Va agar odamlarga o`lchab yoki tortib bersalar, kamaytirarlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,65]}]}

{"text":"6. U kunda odamlar olamlarning \nRobbi huzurida tik turarlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,60]}]}

{"text":"8. Sijjiyn qanday narsa ekanini senga nima bildirdi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,55]}]}

{"text":"12. Uni haddan oshuvchi va o`ta gunohkorlardan boshqalar yolg`onga chiqarmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,80]}]}

{"text":"13. Qachon unga oyatlarimiz tilovat qilinsa, \navvalgilarning afsonalari, der.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,79]}]}

{"text":"14. Yo`q! Ularning qilgan kasblari qalblariga \nmog`or bo`lib o`rnashib qolgandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,81]}]}

{"text":"15. Yo`q!!! Albatta, ular o`sha kunda o`z \nRobbilarini ko`rishdan to`silurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,78]}]}

{"text":"17. So`ngra, mana bu, sizlar yolg`onga chiqarib yurgan narsa, deyilur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,70]}]}

{"text":"19. Illiyyiyn qandoq narsa ekanini senga nima bildirdi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,58]}]}

{"text":"23. Pardali baland so`rilar ustida nazar solib tururlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,56]}]}

{"text":"26. U(sharob)ning xotimasi miskdandir. \nVa shu narsa uchun musobaqa qiluvchilar musobaqa qilsinlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,99]}]}

{"text":"29. Albatta, jinoyat qilganlar iymon keltirganlar ustidan kular edilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,71]}]}

{"text":"30. Agar mo`minlar ularning yonidan o`tsalar, masxaralab ishora qilar edilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,77]}]}

{"text":"31. Agar (kofirlar) o`z ahllari huzuriga qaytib borsalar, huzurlanib qaytib borar edilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,89]}]}

{"text":"32. Va agar u(mo`min)larni ko`rsalar, \nAlbatta, anavilar adashganlar, der edilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,83]}]}

{"text":"33. Holbuki, ular mo`minlar ustidan kuzatuvchi qilib yuborilganlari yo`q-ku!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"34. Endi, bu Kunda iymon keltirganlar kofirlar ustidan kularlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"36. Kofirlar bu dunyoda qilgan ishlarining\n savobini olarmikanlar?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,69]}]}
